    "The model was trained with intercalated validation steps and its performance was evaluated using Leave One Out crossvalidation.",
    "The generative model achieved lower reconstruction errors than the chosen benchmarks (Table 1; see also Fig. 4).",
    "We also trained the same model using brain networks obtained without the hybrid tracking pipeline (see Methods).",
    "Interestingly, results were slightly worse (Table S2; see also Table S3), suggesting that our hybrid method is equivalent if not better than current state-of-the-art fiber reconstruction pipelines.",
